
Check Disk Space
df - Report file system disk space usage.
Syntax: df [options] [file]

Find Largest Folders
du - Estimate file space usage.
Syntax: du [options] [file]
du -h /path/to/directory

combine du with sort and head.
du -ah /path/to/directory | sort -rh | head -n 10

du -ah /path/to/directory: Calculate disk usage for all files and folders in the specified directory, with human-readable output.
sort -rh: Sort the output in reverse order (largest to smallest) and in human-readable format.
head -n 10: Display the top 10 results.
